<plot>A variety of Russian stars are presented in a revue that includes many traditional songs and dances. Among the acts in this 31-minute short are: The Red Army Ensemble doing "The Red Army Anniversary Song" and "Cavalry Dance"; a ballet skit called "The Skating Dance" by Anna Redel and Mikhail Krustalev; "Lilac Blossoms" by Lidiya Ruslanova; a production number by the Piatnitsky Ensemble, and "Quadrille", a Russian folk dance.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?377911</url></doc>
